plot: Officer Nolan and Celina take on a special case. Monica enlists help to identify her attackers. Lopez and Harper discover a connection to the trail of crimes.

Nolan and Celina uncover crucial evidence in Maddogg's apartment, leading them to a mysterious notebook. Meanwhile, Chen takes on an undercover assignment posing as a babysitter, inadvertently finding out who she is babysitting for is linked to Monica. As the team delves deeper into the investigation, Monica meets with Oskar to gather more intel on the break-in at her house. Amidst the chaos, Nolan struggles to bridge the gap with Celina, while Smitty uncovers a list of individuals connected to Blair London. With each revelation, the team faces mounting challenges and dangerous adversaries, pushing them to their limits in the pursuit of justice.—Austin Moore
